cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the problem of multi-class novelty detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The proposed method involves the use of a novel loss function and a segregation network, which are relevant to the field of deep learning (cs.MM).
